{"tid":961480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭祝賀劉德華演唱會成功","createTime":"2018-12-30T07:02:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T01:00:57.000Z","uid":184679,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"97e2f3ddc265beed66f830a4d9725d415bb11802","tid":961480,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:02:05.000Z","msg":"早前劉德華為團結香港基金宣傳短片擔任旁白，力撐明日大嶼填海而被網民圍攻。林鄭月娥今年10月喺《施政報告》記者會上就主動為華仔抱不平，覺得華仔拍片都係因為關心下一代發展，又話有人因為短片侮辱華仔係非常之唔公道。林鄭當時仲話：「對劉先生能敢於表達自己意見表示敬佩，預祝佢12月演唱會成功。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181229/large/1546074390_2669.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181229%2Flarge%2F1546074390_2669.png&h=afdf926e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181229/59083672\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181229%2F59083672&d=64hfh1fhp%2Fb782P9UO5lbdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=07496fc3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181229%2F59083672&h=708c79ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181229/59083672</a>"},{"pid":"971d80b6cdeafc5abcb1d7661d23ac875bcdbb77","tid":961480,"uid":20816,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T07:03:55.000Z","msg":"點解稱中國係支那就唔係勇於表達自己?<br />\n更要DQ？"},{"pid":"38aa7351ec5445f3f7590a7bc098794c67c48e6c","tid":961480,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T08:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c6ce58f4e9e2e06f8fded60e968d5c0bdd44954","tid":961480,"uid":213441,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-30T09:02:08.000Z","msg":"死亡祝福"},{"pid":"17524d5e8f836c93a2a8ffe4c7de364af9c68ef6","tid":961480,"uid":121580,"like":0,